data.title: Kelly Johnson
data.meta_description: Kelly Johnson. Self: Braves TBS Baseball. Kelly Johnson was born on 22 February 1982 in Austin, Texas, USA. He has been married to Lauren Thacker since 26 January 2008. They have three children.
data.text: IF/OF taken by the Atlanta Braves 38th overall in the 2000 MLB draft out of Westwood High School (Austin, TX). Has played for the Braves (2005-2009), the Arizona Diamondbacks (2009-2011), the Toronto Blue Jays (2011-2012), the Tampa Bay Rays (2012-2013), the New York Yankees (2014), the Boston Red Sox (2014), the Baltimore Orioles (2014), the Braves (2015), and the New York Mets (2015).
